C4%83ng-c%E1%BA%A3m-th%C3%A0nh/poem-L49q_OKJuuCOqUFx7yebkg">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Bái yết Sơn Lăng cảm thành” - 奉和御製拜謁山陵感成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Ph%C3%BA/author-6psImpn4SbleLfrcnYcyQA">Phạm Đạo Phú</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Th%C3%A1i-kh%E1%BB%89-3/poem-BxeH7lGqyrlGvPh-WYIW0Q">Thái khỉ 3 - 采芑 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-Kinh-Nam-thu%E1%BA%ADt-ho%C3%A0i-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-GrO2vAOFDwGICb-JExBRKA">Thu nhật Kinh Nam thuật hoài tam thập vận - 秋日荊南述懷三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/U-Ch%C3%A2u-H%E1%BB%93-m%C3%A3-kh%C3%A1ch-ca/poem-bTf_52UQUpmjhfVHO5qnaA">U Châu Hồ mã khách ca - 幽州胡馬客歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br></div>	</div>
